---
title: Chargrilled Beef Fillet & Currant Couscous with BBQ Lemony Greens & Zesty Mayo
description: You better call in reinforcements because this dinner is more of a feast! Keep spirits high with a tender beef eye fillet
spread including a fluffy couscous popping with currants and toasted almonds. Best to fire up that BBQ now before
tummies start grumbling!
